# Skill build artifacts
# design/ — skill-builder-pro design-phase scratch folders
**/skills/*/design/
# output/ — intermediate build output inside skill dirs
**/skills/*/output/
# reference/ and references/ — local reference snapshots pulled during builds
**/skills/*/reference/
**/skills/*/references/
# *-workspace/ — iterative eval workspaces generated during skill development
**/skills/*-workspace/
# evals/ — eval run artifacts inside skill and workspace dirs
**/skills/*/evals/
**/skills/*-workspace/evals/
